48
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:42,140
What?

49
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:43,900
- Pursue a girl?
- Pursue a girl?

50
00:02:44,940 --> 00:02:45,660
Keep your voice down.

51
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:50,500
Your Highness,
do you have a crush on someone?

52
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:51,860
Of course.

53
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,140
His Highness was like that last night.

54
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:54,180
