all the time.

59
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:08,340
Come here.

60
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:14,220
Tell me about it.

61
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,220
I just

62
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:16,580
pulled her hair

63
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,740
and put caterpillars in her clothes.

64
00:03:19,220 --> 00:03:19,980
And then...

65
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,140
And then what?

66
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,620
And then he got beat up for sure.

67
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:24,060
You deserved it.

68
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:25,220
Stop it.

69
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,500
Why are you sitting here?
Who allowed you to sit here?

70
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,460
You are both useless to me.

71
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:34,460
I'm furious.

72
00:03:35,220 --> 00:03:36,020
So annoying.

73
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,180
Go away.

74
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:38,700
Get out.

75
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:39,740
Go away.

76
