78
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:54,460
You asked them for suggestions?

79
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,260
Of course,
you won't get any helpful suggestions.

80
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:58,820
They don't know anything about women.

81
00:03:59,220 --> 00:03:59,940
And you do?

82
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:02,180
Yao, let me tell you.

83
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,580
The most important thing
when pursuing a girl is

84
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,940
to protect her every step of the way
all the time.

85
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:10,380
Don't let her get away from you.

86
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:13,220
Right.

87
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:15,740
You do know about women. Tell me more.

88
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:16,740
Imagine this.

89
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:19,100
On a dark and windy night,

90
00:04:19,900 --> 00:04:21,460
you sneak up behind her.

91
00:04:23,060 --> 00:04:25,260
You follow her steps.

92
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:28,140
When she walks fast, you walk fast.

93
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:31,540
Never let her get away from you.

94
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:35,820
Doing something like this,

95
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,540
