she's being followed by a pervert,

98
00:04:41,660 --> 00:04:42,860
you jump right out

99
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:43,900
and tell her,

100
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:45,620
"I am right here.

101
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:46,900
Don't be afraid."

102
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,820
