104
00:04:57,740 --> 00:04:58,620
Prepare her presents.

105
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,660
It's worth a try.

106
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:06,380
How about this?

107
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,380
Yao, tell me

108
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:09,340
what hobbies or skills she has.

109
00:05:09,940 --> 00:05:11,020
I'll help you with your presents.

110
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,140
Hobbies?

111
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:24,020
[Chongwen Academy]

112
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:26,420
Yao,

113
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:28,380
this took me a lot of effort to get.

114
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:29,860
Even knives and fire can't destroy it.

115
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:30,860
A very amazing rope.

116
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:32,860
You can use it to climb or escape.

117
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:36,060
Yao.

118
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:38,420
You aren't giving this to a girl,
are you?

119
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:40,100
Only professional thieves use this.

120
00:05:40,860 --> 00:05:42,260
Don't worry about it. Go back to class.

121
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,220
The Grand Tutor is waiting inside.

122
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:44,420
Yao.

123
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:45,860
It's...

124
