139
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:47,060
Just tell me how to do it.

140
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:50,740
Your Highness, leave it to me.

141
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:57,260
I didn't know

142
00:06:57,380 --> 00:06:59,460
