143
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,540
His Highness said

144
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,820
that I must see you open it yourself,
Miss Mei.

145
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:13,860
His Highness was really patient.

146
00:07:29,020 --> 00:07:30,700
I'll know what it is once I open it.

147
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:37,060
It's...

148
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:45,420
Go on.

149
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:49,380
Tell His Highness,
thanks for his present.

150
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:51,180
You may leave now.

151
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:52,460
I...

152
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:58,180
Class begins, students.

153
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:01,340
There is now a new seating arrangement.

154
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:03,340
The Grand Tutor
arranged it himself this time.

155
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:04,500
Well...

156
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:05,260
A new one.

157
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:06,460
- Let's check it out.
- A new one.

158
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:07,620
- Let me see it.
- Let me see it.

159
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:08,500
Let me see where I'll sit.

160
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,540
- Where will I sit?
- Where will I sit?

161
00:08:09,540 --> 00:08:10,740
- Let me take a look.
- Let me take a look.

162
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,780
Why am I still in the last row?

163
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:12,540
You are satisfied, aren't you?

164
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:13,260
Take a seat.

165
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:14,260
- Pin, you're in the first row.
- Sit down.

166
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,980
- I'm so mad.
- Where do I sit?

167
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:17,900
I'll accept the new arrangement.

168
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,500
- We sit together again.
- Why here again?

169
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:20,940
